reviews.text: Great location, rooms are small and capsule like, but the beds were way too hard to sleep on.
Good location, good staff, small rooms. It's good value for money.
Spacious room, friendly and helpful staff. Very good location and you can catch the free airport shuttle from HK station to the  Regal hotel just around the corner. Will definitely be coming back.

This hotels need to improve on the cleanliness. My room was dusty as in someone hasn’t been living there for quite some time. The airduct on the bedroom and bathroom was full of dusts.
There’s a promotion in the afternoon at the lounge bar, buy 1 get 1, something that you have to try. The bartender makes a good cocktail and they’re friendly.

Nothing positive expect location. Got bug stings and rashes over skin after staying two night & had to switch to another hotel. The hotel staff reacted with very slow & negative attitude. Poor interior lighting & breakfast, NOT recommended & NOT even close to a 4-star level.

result.formatted_address: 香港銅鑼灣邊寧頓街15號
result.name: Wheatfield Kitchen

reviews.text:
今日黎到一間叫麥田廚房係一間上海俄羅斯菜，裝修都幾特別，放左好多一系列既暴力熊公仔

首先黎左個上海派招牌羅宋湯，同出面一般既羅宋湯唔同，佢係比較濃稠的，每一啖都有牛肉同蔬菜，唔會太酸，唔會太甜，好好飲。

而我個主菜就香煎三文魚柳番茄刁草醬配意粉（$142）
賣相好靚，有唔同既顏色，十分吸引。三文魚外脆內軟，一D都唔腥，仲有個番茄汁先係最好美既，酸酸甜甜的，因為本人好鍾意食番茄，所以覺得好好食~
仲有D薯菜係新鮮炸的，熱辣辣的，正~
Nice food with reasonable price.   Good location,  modern and simple decos.  Very clean and not so crowded.  Friendly staff.

Was there for lunch today. Pleasant surprise. Cheal set lunch around $160. Excellent Russian soup 羅宋湯 plus tasty and tender Russian roast beef. Extremely good value for money. Setting is no frills but comfortable. Service is ok too.

I haven't been here for more than 3 years after I changed my job.
The Russian Soup is still so nice!
The best in Hong Kong!
Suggest to go during lunch hour. Much better price!!!!
喜歡羅宋湯的要必試，我就好鍾意，叫了帶子和牛柳絲炒意粉，帶子煎得剛剛好，牛柳絲一點也不韌，好味道👍🏻
